{
  "video_id": "wgPLG_1BvQo",
  "title": "My courtroom battle with a Holocaust denier | Dr. Deborah E. Lipstadt | TEDxSkoll",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 17682.0,
      "end_time": 21789.0,
      "text": "I come to you today to speak of liars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 21789.0,
      "end_time": 23236.0,
      "text": "lawsuits"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 23236.0,
      "end_time": 25510.0,
      "text": "and laughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25510.0,
      "end_time": 28644.0,
      "text": "The first time I heard about Holocaust denial,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28644.0,
      "end_time": 30570.0,
      "text": "I laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30570.0,
      "end_time": 32787.0,
      "text": "Holocaust denial?"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32787.0,
      "end_time": 36241.0,
      "text": "The Holocaust which has the dubious distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36241.0,
      "end_time": 41646.0,
      "text": "of being the best-documented genocide in the world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41646.0,
      "end_time": 44706.0,
      "text": "Who could believe it didn&#39;t happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44706.0,
      "end_time": 46857.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46857.0,
      "end_time": 49162.0,
      "text": "For deniers to be right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49162.0,
      "end_time": 51611.0,
      "text": "who would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51611.0,
      "end_time": 54401.0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, the victims --"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54401.0,
      "end_time": 60321.0,
      "text": "the survivors who have told us their harrowing stories."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60321.0,
      "end_time": 62659.0,
      "text": "Who else would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62659.0,
      "end_time": 64636.0,
      "text": "The bystanders."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 64635.99999999999,
      "end_time": 68638.0,
      "text": "The people who lived in the myriads of towns and villages and cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68638.0,
      "end_time": 70634.0,
      "text": "on the Eastern front,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70634.0,
      "end_time": 73100.0,
      "text": "who watched their neighbors be rounded up --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73100.0,
      "end_time": 76337.0,
      "text": "men, women, children, young, old --"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76337.0,
      "end_time": 79081.0,
      "text": "and be marched to the outskirts of the town"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79081.0,
      "end_time": 82585.0,
      "text": "to be shot and left dead in ditches."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82585.0,
      "end_time": 83939.0,
      "text": "Or the Poles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 83939.0,
      "end_time": 88644.0,
      "text": "who lived in towns and villages around the death camps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88644.0,
      "end_time": 91044.0,
      "text": "who watched day after day"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 91044.0,
      "end_time": 93810.0,
      "text": "as the trains went in filled with people"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93810.0,
      "end_time": 96387.0,
      "text": "and came out empty."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96387.0,
      "end_time": 100605.0,
      "text": "But above all, who would have to be wrong?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 100605.0,
      "end_time": 102712.0,
      "text": "The perpetrators."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 102712.0,
      "end_time": 106079.0,
      "text": "The people who say, &quot;We did it."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 106079.0,
      "end_time": 107627.0,
      "text": "I did it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107627.0,
      "end_time": 109800.0,
      "text": "Now, maybe they add a caveat."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 109800.0,
      "end_time": 114704.0,
      "text": "They say, &quot;I didn&#39;t have a choice; I was forced to do it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 114704.0,
      "end_time": 118538.0,
      "text": "But nonetheless, they say, &quot;I did it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 118538.0,
      "end_time": 120113.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 120113.0,
      "end_time": 126076.0,
      "text": "In not one war crimes trial since the end of World War II"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126076.0,
      "end_time": 133678.0,
      "text": "has a perpetrator of any nationality ever said, &quot;It didn&#39;t happen.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 133678.0,
      "end_time": 138284.0,
      "text": "Again, they may have said, &quot;I was forced,&quot; but never that it didn&#39;t happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 138284.0,
      "end_time": 139782.0,
      "text": "Having thought that through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139782.0,
      "end_time": 143757.0,
      "text": "I decided denial was not going to be on my agenda;"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 143757.0,
      "end_time": 147489.0,
      "text": "I had bigger things to worry about, to write about, to research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 147489.0,
      "end_time": 149511.0,
      "text": "and I moved on."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149511.0,
      "end_time": 152354.0,
      "text": "Fast-forward a little over a decade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152354.0,
      "end_time": 154190.0,
      "text": "and two senior scholars --"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154190.0,
      "end_time": 157372.0,
      "text": "two of the most prominent historians of the Holocaust --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 157372.0,
      "end_time": 158653.0,
      "text": "approached me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158653.0,
      "end_time": 160466.0,
      "text": "&quot;Deborah, let&#39;s have coffee."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160466.0,
      "end_time": 164087.0,
      "text": "We have a research idea that we think is perfect for you.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 164087.0,
      "end_time": 167944.0,
      "text": "Intrigued and flattered that they came to me with an idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 167944.0,
      "end_time": 169545.0,
      "text": "and thought me worthy of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169545.0,
      "end_time": 172265.0,
      "text": "I asked, &quot;What is it?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172265.0,
      "end_time": 175953.0,
      "text": "And they said, &quot;Holocaust denial.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 175953.0,
      "end_time": 178936.0,
      "text": "And for the second time, I laughed."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 178936.0,
      "end_time": 180884.0,
      "text": "Holocaust denial?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 180884.0,
      "end_time": 182894.0,
      "text": "The Flat Earth folks?"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182894.0,
      "end_time": 185055.0,
      "text": "The Elvis-is-alive people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185055.0,
      "end_time": 187926.0,
      "text": "I should study them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 187926.0,
      "end_time": 189267.0,
      "text": "And these two guys said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 189267.0,
      "end_time": 191612.0,
      "text": "&quot;Yeah, we&#39;re intrigued."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 191612.0,
      "end_time": 193208.0,
      "text": "What are they about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 193208.0,
      "end_time": 194982.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s their objective?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 194982.0,
      "end_time": 199356.0,
      "text": "How do they manage to get people to believe what they say?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 199356.0,
      "end_time": 202908.0,
      "text": "So thinking, if they thought it was worthwhile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 202908.0,
      "end_time": 206306.0,
      "text": "I would take a momentary diversion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 206306.0,
      "end_time": 209268.0,
      "text": "maybe a year, maybe two, three, maybe even four --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 209268.0,
      "end_time": 211537.0,
      "text": "in academic terms, that&#39;s momentary."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 211537.0,
      "end_time": 212703.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 212703.0,
      "end_time": 215114.0,
      "text": "We work very slowly."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 215114.0,
      "end_time": 216710.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 216710.0,
      "end_time": 218536.0,
      "text": "And I would look at them."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 218536.0,
      "end_time": 219715.0,
      "text": "So I did."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 219715.0,
      "end_time": 222578.0,
      "text": "I did my research, and I came up with a number of things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 222578.0,
      "end_time": 225195.0,
      "text": "two of which I&#39;d like to share with you today."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 225195.0,
      "end_time": 226552.0,
      "text": "One:"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 226552.0,
      "end_time": 232312.0,
      "text": "deniers are wolves in sheep&#39;s clothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 232312.0,
      "end_time": 235301.0,
      "text": "They are the same: Nazis, Neo-Nazis --"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 235301.0,
      "end_time": 239386.0,
      "text": "you can decide whether you want to put a &quot;Neo&quot; there or not."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239386.0,
      "end_time": 241743.0,
      "text": "But when I looked at them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241743.0,
      "end_time": 246493.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t see any SS-like uniforms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 246493.0,
      "end_time": 249668.0,
      "text": "swastika-like symbols on the wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 249668.0,
      "end_time": 251749.0,
      "text": "Sieg Heil salutes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 251749.0,
      "end_time": 253317.0,
      "text": "none of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 253317.0,
      "end_time": 256211.0,
      "text": "What I found instead"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 256211.0,
      "end_time": 261516.0,
      "text": "were people parading as respectable academics."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 261516.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262761.0,
      "text": "What did they have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 262761.0,
      "end_time": 264483.0,
      "text": "They had an institute."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 264483.0,
      "end_time": 268992.0,
      "text": "An &quot;Institute for Historical Review.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 268992.0,
      "end_time": 271570.0,
      "text": "They had a journal -- a slick journal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 271570.0,
      "end_time": 274998.0,
      "text": "a &quot;Journal of Historical Review.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 274998.0,
      "end_time": 277728.0,
      "text": "One filled with papers --"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 277728.0,
      "end_time": 280523.0,
      "text": "footnote-laden papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 280523.0,
      "end_time": 283100.0,
      "text": "And they had a new name."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 283100.0,
      "end_time": 285292.0,
      "text": "Not Neo-Nazis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 285292.0,
      "end_time": 287806.0,
      "text": "not anti-Semites --"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 287806.0,
      "end_time": 289591.0,
      "text": "revisionists."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 289591.0,
      "end_time": 291830.0,
      "text": "They said, &quot;We are revisionists."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 291830.0,
      "end_time": 294537.0,
      "text": "We are out to do one thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 294537.0,
      "end_time": 298969.0,
      "text": "to revise mistakes in history.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 298969.0,
      "end_time": 304403.0,
      "text": "But all you had to do was go one inch below the surface,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304403.0,
      "end_time": 306334.0,
      "text": "and what did you find there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306334.0,
      "end_time": 308848.0,
      "text": "The same adulation of Hitler,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308848.0,
      "end_time": 310747.0,
      "text": "praise of the Third Reich,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 310747.0,
      "end_time": 314504.0,
      "text": "anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 314504.0,
      "end_time": 316974.0,
      "text": "This is what intrigued me."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 316974.0,
      "end_time": 325330.0,
      "text": "It was anti-Semitism, racism, prejudice, parading as rational discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 325330.0,
      "end_time": 327163.0,
      "text": "The other thing I found --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 327163.0,
      "end_time": 331171.0,
      "text": "and we saw a slide earlier about facts and opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 331171.0,
      "end_time": 334940.0,
      "text": "many of us have been taught to think there are facts and there are opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 334940.0,
      "end_time": 336420.0,
      "text": "after studying deniers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 336420.0,
      "end_time": 338318.0,
      "text": "I think differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 338318.0,
      "end_time": 339990.0,
      "text": "There are facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 339990.0,
      "end_time": 341728.0,
      "text": "there are opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 341728.0,
      "end_time": 344029.0,
      "text": "and there are lies."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 344029.0,
      "end_time": 349445.0,
      "text": "And what deniers want to do is take their lies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 349445.0,
      "end_time": 351101.0,
      "text": "dress them up as opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351101.0,
      "end_time": 353115.0,
      "text": "maybe edgy opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 353115.0,
      "end_time": 355848.0,
      "text": "maybe sort of out-of-the-box opinions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 355848.0,
      "end_time": 357256.0,
      "text": "but then if they&#39;re opinions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 357256.0,
      "end_time": 359412.0,
      "text": "they should be part of the conversation."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 359412.0,
      "end_time": 364185.0,
      "text": "And then they encroach on the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 364185.0,
      "end_time": 365772.0,
      "text": "I published my work --"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 365772.0,
      "end_time": 366970.0,
      "text": "the book was published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366970.0,
      "end_time": 370396.0,
      "text": "&quot;Denying the Holocaust: The Growing Assault on Truth and Memory,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 370396.0,
      "end_time": 372376.0,
      "text": "it came out in many different countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 372376.0,
      "end_time": 374560.0,
      "text": "including here in Penguin UK,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 374560.0,
      "end_time": 379043.0,
      "text": "and I was done with those folks and ready to move on."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 379043.0,
      "end_time": 383314.0,
      "text": "Then came the letter from Penguin UK."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 383314.0,
      "end_time": 387968.0,
      "text": "And for the third time, I laughed ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 387968.0,
      "end_time": 389852.0,
      "text": "mistakenly."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 389852.0,
      "end_time": 391606.0,
      "text": "I opened the letter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 391606.0,
      "end_time": 397518.0,
      "text": "and it informed me that David Irving was bringing a libel suit against me"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 397518.0,
      "end_time": 399139.0,
      "text": "in the United Kingdom"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 399139.0,
      "end_time": 402833.0,
      "text": "for calling him a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 402833.0,
      "end_time": 404791.0,
      "text": "David Irving suing me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 404791.0,
      "end_time": 406019.0,
      "text": "Who was David Irving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 406019.0,
      "end_time": 408650.0,
      "text": "David Irving was a writer of historical works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 408650.0,
      "end_time": 410697.0,
      "text": "most of them about World War II,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 410697.0,
      "end_time": 413940.0,
      "text": "and virtually all of those works took the position"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 413940.0,
      "end_time": 417542.0,
      "text": "that the Nazis were really not so bad,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 417542.0,
      "end_time": 420650.0,
      "text": "and the allies were really not so good."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 420650.0,
      "end_time": 422779.0,
      "text": "And the Jews, whatever happened to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 422779.0,
      "end_time": 425086.0,
      "text": "they sort of deserved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 425086.0,
      "end_time": 426601.0,
      "text": "He knew the documents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 426601.0,
      "end_time": 428068.0,
      "text": "he knew the facts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 428068.0,
      "end_time": 431896.0,
      "text": "but he somehow twisted them to get this opinion."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 431896.0,
      "end_time": 434432.0,
      "text": "He hadn&#39;t always been a Holocaust denier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 434432.0,
      "end_time": 436197.0,
      "text": "but in the late &#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 436197.0,
      "end_time": 440397.0,
      "text": "he embraced it with great vigor."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 440397.0,
      "end_time": 444326.0,
      "text": "The reason I laughed also was this was a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 444326.0,
      "end_time": 446284.0,
      "text": "who not only was a Holocaust denier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 446284.0,
      "end_time": 448003.0,
      "text": "but seemed quite proud of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 448003.0,
      "end_time": 449651.0,
      "text": "Here was a man -- and I quote --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449651.0,
      "end_time": 454225.0,
      "text": "who said, &quot;I&#39;m going to sink the battleship Auschwitz.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 454225.0,
      "end_time": 455421.0,
      "text": "Here was a man"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 455421.0,
      "end_time": 460596.0,
      "text": "who pointed to the number tattooed on a survivor&#39;s arm and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 460596.0,
      "end_time": 462212.0,
      "text": "&quot;How much money have you made"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462212.0,
      "end_time": 466429.0,
      "text": "from having that number tattooed on your arm?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 466429.0,
      "end_time": 468361.0,
      "text": "Here was a man who said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 468361.0,
      "end_time": 471341.0,
      "text": "&quot;More people died in Senator Kennedy&#39;s car"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 471341.0,
      "end_time": 472677.0,
      "text": "at Chappaquiddick"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 472677.0,
      "end_time": 476015.0,
      "text": "than died in gas chambers at Auschwitz.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 476015.0,
      "end_time": 480286.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s an American reference, but you can look it up."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 480286.0,
      "end_time": 483324.0,
      "text": "This was not a man who seemed at all ashamed or reticent"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 483324.0,
      "end_time": 486016.0,
      "text": "about being a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 486016.0,
      "end_time": 489820.0,
      "text": "Now, lots of my academic colleagues counseled me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 489820.0,
      "end_time": 491750.0,
      "text": "&quot;Eh, Deborah, just ignore it.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 491750.0,
      "end_time": 495362.0,
      "text": "When I explained you can&#39;t just ignore a libel suit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 495362.0,
      "end_time": 498663.0,
      "text": "they said, &quot;Who&#39;s going to believe him anyway?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 498663.0,
      "end_time": 500767.0,
      "text": "But here was the problem:"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 500767.0,
      "end_time": 506099.0,
      "text": "British law put the onus, put the burden of proof on me"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 506099.0,
      "end_time": 508805.0,
      "text": "to prove the truth of what I said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 508805.0,
      "end_time": 511592.0,
      "text": "in contrast to as it would have been in the United States"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 511592.0,
      "end_time": 513120.0,
      "text": "and in many other countries:"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 513120.0,
      "end_time": 516801.0,
      "text": "on him to prove the falsehood."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 516801.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518286.00000000006,
      "text": "What did that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 518285.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521685.99999999994,
      "text": "That meant if I didn&#39;t fight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 521686.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524671.0,
      "text": "he would win by default."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 524671.0,
      "end_time": 526450.0,
      "text": "And if he won by default,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 526450.0,
      "end_time": 529115.0,
      "text": "he could then legitimately say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 529115.0,
      "end_time": 534475.0,
      "text": "&quot;My David Irving version of the Holocaust is a legitimate version."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 534475.0,
      "end_time": 536683.0,
      "text": "Deborah Lipstadt was found to have libeled me"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 536683.0,
      "end_time": 538654.0,
      "text": "when she called me a Holocaust denier."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 538654.0,
      "end_time": 543106.0,
      "text": "Ipso facto, I, David Irving, am not a Holocaust denier.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 543106.0,
      "end_time": 545311.0,
      "text": "And what is that version?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 545311.0,
      "end_time": 548331.0,
      "text": "There was no plan to murder the Jews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 548331.0,
      "end_time": 550407.0,
      "text": "there were no gas chambers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 550407.0,
      "end_time": 552287.0,
      "text": "there were no mass shootings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 552287.0,
      "end_time": 555482.0,
      "text": "Hitler had nothing to do with any suffering that went on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 555482.0,
      "end_time": 559311.0,
      "text": "and the Jews have made this all up"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 559311.0,
      "end_time": 561733.0,
      "text": "to get money from Germany"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 561733.0,
      "end_time": 563464.0,
      "text": "and to get a state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 563464.0,
      "end_time": 566865.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve done it with the aid and abettance of the allies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 566865.0,
      "end_time": 571340.0,
      "text": "they&#39;ve planted the documents and planted the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 571340.0,
      "end_time": 573744.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t let that stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 573744.0,
      "end_time": 576703.0,
      "text": "and ever face a survivor"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 576703.0,
      "end_time": 578702.0,
      "text": "or a child of survivors."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 578702.0,
      "end_time": 580878.0,
      "text": "I couldn&#39;t let that stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 580878.0,
      "end_time": 586067.0,
      "text": "and consider myself a responsible historian."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 586067.0,
      "end_time": 587836.0,
      "text": "So we fought."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 587836.0,
      "end_time": 590142.0,
      "text": "And for those of you who haven&#39;t seen &quot;Denial,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 590142.0,
      "end_time": 591325.0,
      "text": "spoiler alert:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 591325.0,
      "end_time": 592567.0,
      "text": "we won."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 592567.0,
      "end_time": 593886.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 593886.0,
      "end_time": 600868.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 600868.0,
      "end_time": 605133.0,
      "text": "The judge found David Irving"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 605133.0,
      "end_time": 608488.0,
      "text": "to be a liar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 608488.0,
      "end_time": 609675.0,
      "text": "a racist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 609675.0,
      "end_time": 610953.0,
      "text": "an anti-Semite."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 610953.0,
      "end_time": 613337.0,
      "text": "His view of history was tendentious,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 613337.0,
      "end_time": 615287.0,
      "text": "he lied, he distorted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 615287.0,
      "end_time": 617954.0,
      "text": "and most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 617954.0,
      "end_time": 620091.0,
      "text": "he did it deliberately."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 620091.0,
      "end_time": 624254.0,
      "text": "We showed a pattern, in over 25 different major instances."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 624254.0,
      "end_time": 627388.0,
      "text": "Not small things -- many of us in this audience write books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 627388.0,
      "end_time": 628597.0,
      "text": "are writing books;"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 628597.0,
      "end_time": 632087.0,
      "text": "we always make mistakes, that&#39;s why we&#39;re glad to have second editions:"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 632087.0,
      "end_time": 633297.0,
      "text": "correct the mistakes."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 633297.0,
      "end_time": 635514.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 635514.0,
      "end_time": 639498.0,
      "text": "But these always moved in the same direction:"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 639498.0,
      "end_time": 641733.0,
      "text": "blame the Jews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 641733.0,
      "end_time": 644580.0,
      "text": "exonerate the Nazis."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 644580.0,
      "end_time": 647076.0,
      "text": "But how did we win?"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 647076.0,
      "end_time": 653070.0,
      "text": "What we did is follow his footnotes back to his sources."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 653070.0,
      "end_time": 654877.0,
      "text": "And what did we find?"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 654877.0,
      "end_time": 656380.0,
      "text": "Not in most cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 656380.0,
      "end_time": 658372.0,
      "text": "and not in the preponderance of cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 658372.0,
      "end_time": 662707.0,
      "text": "but in every single instance where he made some reference to the Holocaust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 662707.0,
      "end_time": 666973.0,
      "text": "that his supposed evidence was distorted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 666973.0,
      "end_time": 668417.0,
      "text": "half-truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 668417.0,
      "end_time": 669775.0,
      "text": "date-changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 669775.0,
      "end_time": 671986.0,
      "text": "sequence-changed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 671986.0,
      "end_time": 674134.0,
      "text": "someone put at a meeting who wasn&#39;t there."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 674134.0,
      "end_time": 676919.0,
      "text": "In other words, he didn&#39;t have the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 676919.0,
      "end_time": 679052.0,
      "text": "His evidence didn&#39;t prove it."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 679052.0,
      "end_time": 682508.0,
      "text": "We didn&#39;t prove what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 682508.0,
      "end_time": 685031.0,
      "text": "We proved that what he said happened --"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 685031.0,
      "end_time": 687915.0,
      "text": "and by extension, all deniers, because he either quotes them"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 687915.0,
      "end_time": 690410.0,
      "text": "or they get their arguments from him --"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 690410.0,
      "end_time": 691680.0,
      "text": "is not true."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 691680.0,
      "end_time": 692893.0,
      "text": "What they claim --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 692893.0,
      "end_time": 697489.0,
      "text": "they don&#39;t have the evidence to prove it."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 697489.0,
      "end_time": 702257.0,
      "text": "So why is my story more than just the story"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 702257.0,
      "end_time": 706088.0,
      "text": "of a quirky, long, six-year, difficult lawsuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 706088.0,
      "end_time": 711101.0,
      "text": "an American professor being dragged into a courtroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 711101.0,
      "end_time": 714169.0,
      "text": "by a man that the court declared in its judgment"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 714169.0,
      "end_time": 716443.0,
      "text": "was a Neo-Nazi polemicist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 716443.0,
      "end_time": 718680.0,
      "text": "What message does it have?"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 718680.0,
      "end_time": 721677.0,
      "text": "I think in the context of the question of truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 721677.0,
      "end_time": 724163.0,
      "text": "it has a very significant message."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 724163.0,
      "end_time": 725972.0,
      "text": "Because today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 725972.0,
      "end_time": 727662.0,
      "text": "as we well know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 727662.0,
      "end_time": 732582.0,
      "text": "truth and facts are under assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 732582.0,
      "end_time": 735858.0,
      "text": "Social media, for all the gifts it has given us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 735858.0,
      "end_time": 741463.0,
      "text": "has also allowed the difference between facts -- established facts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 741463.0,
      "end_time": 743244.0,
      "text": "and lies"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 743244.0,
      "end_time": 745870.0,
      "text": "to be flattened."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 745870.0,
      "end_time": 747404.0,
      "text": "Third of all:"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 747404.0,
      "end_time": 749592.0,
      "text": "extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 749592.0,
      "end_time": 753468.0,
      "text": "You may not see Ku Klux Klan robes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 753468.0,
      "end_time": 755563.0,
      "text": "you may not see burning crosses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 755563.0,
      "end_time": 759906.0,
      "text": "you may not even hear outright white supremacist language."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 759906.0,
      "end_time": 764836.0,
      "text": "It may go by names: &quot;alt-right,&quot; &quot;National Front&quot; -- pick your names."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 764836.0,
      "end_time": 770695.0,
      "text": "But underneath, it&#39;s that same extremism that I found in Holocaust denial"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 770695.0,
      "end_time": 776014.0,
      "text": "parading as rational discourse."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 776014.0,
      "end_time": 781255.0,
      "text": "We live in an age where truth is on the defensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 781255.0,
      "end_time": 783763.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m reminded of a New Yorker cartoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 783763.0,
      "end_time": 786307.0,
      "text": "A quiz show recently appeared in &quot;The New Yorker&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 786307.0,
      "end_time": 789553.0,
      "text": "where the host of the quiz show is saying to one of the contestants,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 789553.0,
      "end_time": 791886.0,
      "text": "&quot;Yes, ma&#39;am, you had the right answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 791886.0,
      "end_time": 794403.0,
      "text": "But your opponent yelled more loudly than you did,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 794403.0,
      "end_time": 797108.0,
      "text": "so he gets the point.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 797108.0,
      "end_time": 799437.0,
      "text": "What can we do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 799437.0,
      "end_time": 800838.0,
      "text": "First of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 800838.0,
      "end_time": 806293.0,
      "text": "we cannot be beguiled by rational appearances."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 806293.0,
      "end_time": 808086.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve got to look underneath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 808086.0,
      "end_time": 811871.0,
      "text": "and we will find there the extremism."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 811871.0,
      "end_time": 813881.0,
      "text": "Second of all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 813881.0,
      "end_time": 822017.0,
      "text": "we must understand that truth is not relative."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 822017.0,
      "end_time": 823505.0,
      "text": "Number three,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 823505.0,
      "end_time": 827218.0,
      "text": "we must go on the offensive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 827218.0,
      "end_time": 829556.0,
      "text": "not the defensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 829556.0,
      "end_time": 832187.0,
      "text": "When someone makes an outrageous claim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 832187.0,
      "end_time": 835715.0,
      "text": "even though they may hold one of the highest offices in the land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 835715.0,
      "end_time": 837750.0,
      "text": "if not the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 837750.0,
      "end_time": 839284.0,
      "text": "we must say to them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 839284.0,
      "end_time": 841274.0,
      "text": "&quot;Where&#39;s the proof?"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 841274.0,
      "end_time": 843435.0,
      "text": "Where&#39;s the evidence?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 843435.0,
      "end_time": 846386.0,
      "text": "We must hold their feet to the fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 846386.0,
      "end_time": 852275.0,
      "text": "We must not treat it as if their lies are the same as the facts."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 852275.0,
      "end_time": 855839.0,
      "text": "And as I said earlier, truth is not relative."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 855839.0,
      "end_time": 858719.0,
      "text": "Many of us have grown up in the world of the academy"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 858719.0,
      "end_time": 860484.0,
      "text": "and enlightened liberal thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 860484.0,
      "end_time": 864044.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re taught everything is open to debate."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 864044.0,
      "end_time": 866082.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not the case."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 866082.0,
      "end_time": 870072.0,
      "text": "There are certain things that are true."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 870072.0,
      "end_time": 873116.0,
      "text": "There are indisputable facts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 873116.0,
      "end_time": 875399.0,
      "text": "objective truths."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 875399.0,
      "end_time": 880240.0,
      "text": "Galileo taught it to us centuries ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 880240.0,
      "end_time": 884931.0,
      "text": "Even after being forced to recant by the Vatican"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 884931.0,
      "end_time": 887528.0,
      "text": "that the Earth moved around the Sun,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 887528.0,
      "end_time": 888706.0,
      "text": "he came out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 888706.0,
      "end_time": 891040.0,
      "text": "and what is he reported to have said?"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 891040.0,
      "end_time": 896222.0,
      "text": "&quot;And yet, it still moves.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 896222.0,
      "end_time": 899086.0,
      "text": "The Earth is not flat."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 899086.0,
      "end_time": 902267.0,
      "text": "The climate is changing."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 902267.0,
      "end_time": 904559.0,
      "text": "Elvis is not alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 904559.0,
      "end_time": 906118.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 906118.0,
      "end_time": 908458.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 908458.0,
      "end_time": 910783.0,
      "text": "And most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 910783.0,
      "end_time": 916169.0,
      "text": "truth and fact are under assault."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 916169.0,
      "end_time": 917803.0,
      "text": "The job ahead of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 917803.0,
      "end_time": 919030.0,
      "text": "the task ahead of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 919030.0,
      "end_time": 920648.0,
      "text": "the challenge ahead of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 920648.0,
      "end_time": 922627.0,
      "text": "is great."
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 922627.0,
      "end_time": 926121.0,
      "text": "The time to fight is short."
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 926121.0,
      "end_time": 929809.0,
      "text": "We must act now."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 929809.0,
      "end_time": 933078.0,
      "text": "Later will be too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 933078.0,
      "end_time": 934364.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 934364.0,
      "end_time": 944364.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}